<h1 update_tag>Update a tag</h1>

<p>Modify tag information.</p>

<pre>[PUT] <hl>/api/v1/tags/:id</hl></pre>

<h2 update_tag_request_body>Request body</h2>

<table>
  <tr>
    <th>Field</th>
    <th>Type</th>
    <th>Required</th>
    <th>Range</th>
    <th>Description</th>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td><tt>name</tt></td>
    <td><tt>string</tt></td>
    <td><tt>false</tt></td>
    <td><tt>length: [1, 64]</tt></td>
    <td>New tag name.</td>
  </tr>
</table>

<h2 update_tag_example>Example</h2>

<pre>
curl -X PUT \
  --oauth2-bearer AUTH_TOKEN \
  --data-urlencode 'name=php8.4' \
  http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tags/:id
</pre>

